WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:04.650
Gerda has told Anna and Karl about 
 a planned German-French Falcon's camp.

00:04.700 --> 00:06.500
The two are immediately thrilled.

00:06.500 --> 00:08.900
They have never met French children before.

00:09.000 --> 00:14.400
They are curious and and would like to help
 bring about a peaceful coexistence between the two nations.

00:14.500 --> 00:18.900
Because the war has only brought
 more misery to all the workers.
